author: Adam K. Raymond
title: Sorry Guys, Ronda Rousey Has a Boyfriend
text:
Before today, Travis Browne was probably best known as the giant UFC fighter whose ex-girlfriend accused him of beating her up this summer. Or maybe as the guy who got TKO'd by Bigfoot Silva in 2012. Either way, he's about to have a new title: Ronda Rousey's boyfriend.
As the 6'7" heavyweight tells TMZ : "She's my woman and I am her man."
Browne's last girlfriend was fitness model Jenna Renee Webb, who made waves in July when she posted pictures of bruises on her arms and neck and accused Browne of domestic abuse .
Browne vehemently denied those accusations, and a UFC investigation eventually exonerated him in the eyes of the promotion.
But now that relationship is over and Browne tells TMZ he and Rousey are officially an item. "There's no boyfriend, girlfriend stuff ... we're together," he said.
Now Browne must begin the most difficult part of dating Rousey: winning over her mom .
